item.title: Bill's Cafe
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Daytime dining is our specialty! We begin each day at the crack of dawn, slicing fresh fruits, squeezing fresh orange juice, baking croissants and cinnamon rolls, and whipping up our home-made soups from scratch. Our extensive breakfast menu covers all of the classic breakfast traditions, along with an extensive selection of creative specialties. And if you start the day late, you can rest assured knowing that breakfast at Bill's is served all day, along with a wide choice of lunch items, ranging from classic sandwiches, to salads, to our daily chef's specials. The food comes big and hearty — with quality preparation, fresh ingredients, and the friendliest service around. So come on in and spend time with your family and ours. We look forward to serving you soon!!

item.title: Sir Winston Churchill's
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: SIR WINSTON CHURCHILL'S was created in 1972 by Rey Fernandez and his English wife Jane Pearson. They transformed a Tudor-style family mansion in Polanco into a well loved Restaurant that has become a famous landmark in Mexico City. Churchill's continues to amaze new customers as well as it's faithful clientele alike with the outstanding quality of it's food and a dedicated service for over 40 years. The delicious meals which include traditional favourites like Beef Wellington and Prime Rib of Roast Beef compete with the new daily specialities created by Churchill's talented Chef from France. A visit to Churchill's is an experience to be savoured as it is a true oasis in the very heart of Mexico City.
